snippet.title: acai cOrner - 3 Endings - Be a Magical Girl & Use Your Guitar as a Weapon | Indie Horror Games
snippet.description:
"A short adventure-spooky game!"

Your name is Mizuki.
You have fallen into the sewers.
You find your favorite guitar!
You feel different. You are a magical girl now.
There are monsters everywhere.
It gets harder to breathe the further you go...
You must escape.

A Game by Moca (Team Shibu).
